data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 6.8-acre parcel of land this charming ranch offers a spacious layout boasting 5 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Providing ample space for relaxation and hosting guests. The interior exudes warmth and modern character, with tasteful updates throughout. Add on the finishing touches to make it your own. Outside, the expansive grounds offer endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. Whether you're exploring the wooded areas, cultivating a garden, or simply soaking in the serene surroundings, this property is a nature lover's paradise. Conveniently located just a short drive from amenities and recreational opportunities, yet secluded enough to enjoy the peace and quiet of rural living. Schedule your tour today!
